    <!-- PAGE 2: DEDICATION -->
    <div class="page dedication-page hidden" id="page-1">
      <div class="page-inner">
        <div class="ded-for">For</div>
        <div class="ded-name">the Ducklings.</div>
        <div class="ded-egg">🐣</div>
        <div class="ded-note">Everything I do and everything I become is because of you.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="page-num">iii</div>
    </div>

    <!-- PAGE 3: FOREWORD -->
    <div class="page hidden" id="page-2">
      <div class="page-inner">
        <div class="section-label" style="text-align:center">Foreword</div>
        <hr class="page-rule">
        <div class="body-text" style="font-family:'Lora',serif;font-style:italic;font-size:10px;color:var(--ink)">This book is for anyone who ever looked at their life and felt, quietly, privately, that there was supposed to be <em>more.</em></div>
        <div class="body-text">For anyone who had a vision bigger than their circumstances. Who felt a longing they could not name. Who sensed that the path they were on was not the only path.</div>
        <div class="body-text">For anyone who wanted to travel but did not have a map. Who wanted to be free but did not know what freedom looked like, or whether someone like them was allowed to have it.</div>
        <div class="pull-quote"><p>This book is your map. Not a fixed one. A living map that begins with your own nature and ends wherever your nature leads you.</p></div>
        <div class="body-text">The footprints are yours to make. The journey belongs entirely, irreversibly, beautifully to you.</div>
        <div class="body-text">You did not need to be fixed to arrive here. You only needed to be <strong>ready.</strong></div>
        <div style="margin-top:12px;text-align:center">
          <div style="font-family:'Lora',serif;font-style:italic;font-size:9.5px;color:var(--mid);line-height:1.8">You were always ready.<br>You only needed to remember.</div>
          <div style="font-size:9px;font-weight:300;color:var(--dim);margin-top:8px">love,<br>chandanni</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="page-num">iv</div>
    </div>

    <!-- PAGE 4: FROM THE AUTHOR -->
    <div class="page hidden" id="page-3">
      <div class="page-inner">
        <div class="section-label">From the Author</div>
        <div class="page-title">For <em>You</em></div>
        <div class="page-tagline">Because this book found you for a reason.</div>
        <hr class="page-rule">
        <div class="body-text">You did not pick up this book by accident. Nothing in this universe happens by accident. That is not mysticism. That is physics.</div>
        <div class="body-text">I have spent my life at the intersection of ancient intelligence and modern living, watching thousands of people transform. Not because they learned something new. Because they <strong>remembered something they already were.</strong></div>
        <div class="pull-quote"><p>Self mastery is not about becoming someone else. It is about remembering who you already are, and living that, fully, at every stage.</p></div>
        <div class="body-text">This is not a wellness book. It is a <strong>self mastery manual.</strong> Self mastery is not perfection, it is evolution. The high road, available to anyone, at any stage.</div>
        <div class="body-text">Read it slowly. Read it like music. You are already whole.</div>
        <div style="margin-top:10px;font-size:9px;font-weight:300;color:var(--dim)">love, chandanni</div>
      </div>
      <div class="page-num">v</div>
    </div>

    <!-- PAGE 5: CH1 -->
    <div class="page hidden" id="page-4">
      <div class="page-inner">
        <div class="section-label">Chapter One</div>
        <div class="page-title">The Original <em>Biohack</em></div>
        <div class="page-tagline">The original technology of self mastery.</div>
        <hr class="page-rule">
        <svg class="chapter-geo geo" viewBox="0 0 200 200">
          <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="78" fill="none" stroke="#7B2FBE" stroke-width="0.8" opacity="0.3"/>
          <circle cx="100" cy="68" r="32" fill="none" stroke="#7B2FBE" stroke-width="0.9" opacity="0.45"/>
          <circle cx="100" cy="132" r="32" fill="none" stroke="#7B2FBE" stroke-width="0.9" opacity="0.45"/>
          <circle cx="72.3" cy="84" r="32" fill="none" stroke="#7B2FBE" stroke-width="0.9" opacity="0.45"/>
          <circle cx="127.7" cy="84" r="32" fill="none" stroke="#7B2FBE" stroke-width="0.9" opacity="0.45"/>
          <circle cx="72.3" cy="116" r="32" fill="none" stroke="#7B2FBE" stroke-width="0.9" opacity="0.45"/>
          <circle cx="127.7" cy="116" r="32" fill="none" stroke="#7B2FBE" stroke-width="0.9" opacity="0.45"/>
          <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="32" fill="none" stroke="#7B2FBE" stroke-width="0.9" opacity="0.45"/>
          <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="4" fill="#7B2FBE" opacity="0.9"/>
        </svg>
        <div class="body-text">The word biohacking is new. The practice is ancient. Long before wearables, there was Ayurveda, and it knew something modern wellness is only beginning to rediscover.</div>
        <div class="body-text"><strong>The body is intelligent. The universe is intelligent. They speak the same language.</strong></div>
        <div class="insight-box">
          <div class="insight-label">Self Mastery Defined</div>
          <div class="insight-text">Self mastery is not the elimination of flaws. It is the ongoing practice of living in alignment with your deepest nature, your constitution, your dharma, your elemental intelligence. Available to everyone. At every age.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="body-text">Ayurveda offers something radical: a <strong>personalized operating system for being human</strong>, a living, intelligent map, unique to you.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="page-num">1</div>
    </div>

    <!-- PAGE 6: TERM - AYURVEDA -->
    <div class="page hidden" id="page-5">
      <div class="page-inner" style="justify-content:center;gap:10px">
        <svg style="width:80px;height:80px" viewBox="0 0 200 200">
          <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="78" fill="none" stroke="#7B2FBE" stroke-width="0.8" opacity="0.3"/>
          <circle cx="100" cy="68" r="32" fill="none" stroke="#7B2FBE" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.5"/>
          <circle cx="100" cy="132" r="32" fill="none" stroke="#7B2FBE" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.5"/>
          <circle cx="72.3" cy="84" r="32" fill="none" stroke="#7B2FBE" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.5"/>
          <circle cx="127.7" cy="84" r="32" fill="none" stroke="#7B2FBE" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.5"/>
          <circle cx="72.3" cy="116" r="32" fill="none" stroke="#7B2FBE" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.5"/>
          <circle cx="127.7" cy="116" r="32" fill="none" stroke="#7B2FBE" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.5"/>
          <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="32" fill="none" stroke="#7B2FBE" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.5"/>
          <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="4" fill="#7B2FBE"/>
        </svg>
        <div class="term-box" style="width:100%">
          <span class="term-symbol">✦</span>
          <div class="term-name">Ayurveda</div>
          <hr class="term-rule">
          <div class="term-english">The Science of Life</div>
          <span class="term-pron">(AY-ur-vay-duh)</span>
          <div class="term-def">From Sanskrit: Ayus (life) + Veda (knowledge). The 5,000-year-old system of natural healing originating in India. A complete philosophy of conscious living and self mastery, teaching that health is harmony between body, mind, spirit, and the natural world.</div>
        </div>
        <div style="font-family:'Lora',serif;font-style:italic;font-size:9.5px;color:var(--mid);text-align:center;line-height:1.8">The practice of life as a living intelligence.<br>The original self mastery system.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="page-num">2</div>
    </div>

    <!-- PAGE 7: CH2 -->
    <div class="page hidden" id="page-6">
      <div class="page-inner">
        <div class="section-label">Chapter Two</div>
        <div class="page-title">The Five <em>Elements</em></div>
        <div class="page-tagline">The building blocks of self mastery.</div>
        <hr class="page-rule">
        <svg class="chapter-geo geo" viewBox="0 0 200 200">
          <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="82" fill="none" stroke="#7B2FBE" stroke-width="0.7" opacity="0.3"/>
          <polygon points="100,18 182,118 18,118" fill="none" stroke="#7B2FBE" stroke-width="1.2" opacity="0.65"/>
          <polygon points="100,182 182,82 18,82" fill="none" stroke="#7B2FBE" stroke-width="1.2" opacity="0.65"/>
          <polygon points="100,42 162,142 38,142" fill="none" stroke="#7B2FBE" stroke-width="0.7" opacity="0.4"/>
          <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="28" fill="none" stroke="#7B2FBE" stroke-width="0.7" opacity="0.35"/>
          <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="4" fill="#7B2FBE"/>
        </svg>
        <div class="item-list">
          <div><div class="item-key">✦ Space, Akasha</div><div class="item-desc">The container of all things. Silence. Potential.</div></div>
          <div><div class="item-key">〰 Air, Vayu</div><div class="item-desc">Movement. Breath. The principle of motion that animates life.</div></div>
          <div><div class="item-key">△ Fire, Agni</div><div class="item-desc">Transformation. Digestion. Intelligence.</div></div>
          <div><div class="item-key">◯ Water, Jala</div><div class="item-desc">Cohesion. Flow. Emotion. The connective tissue of life.</div></div>
          <div><div class="item-key">⬡ Earth, Prithvi</div><div class="item-desc">Structure. Stability. Form. The principle of matter.</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="pull-quote"><p>Self mastery begins with understanding what you are made of. Not metaphorically, literally.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="page-num">5</div>
    </div>

